				<DIV></DIV>
<P>(AA)</P>
<P>1. Vanquish Undead - Golgolath's holy blade cleanses his target! (13256) says it all</P>
<P>2. Holy Steed - Fastest transport around, gotta love it</P>
<P>3. Act of Valor - Endless comedy value</P>
<P>4. Improved LoH - Much love for healing MT for 16k while he's in the purple</P>
<P>5. Combat Stabilty - A little boring, but one of the most powerful aa's. </P>
<P>(Spell)</P>
<P>1. Ward of Tunare - (i.e. Godmode to the whiners)</P>
<P>2. Ancient: Force of Jeron - When it works</P>
<P>3. Instrument of Nife - What Hulkling said</P>
<P>4. Shackles of Tunare - Rooting like there's no tomorrow ftw</P>
<P>5. Wave of Piety - Not very mana friendly but gets the job done in spades</P>
<P>(Item)</P>
<P>1. Mantle of the Wyrmguard - Free clicky wave heal every 3.5 minutes is just insane</P>
<P>2. Blade of Forgotten Faith - Group heal proc plus tash cure, much love</P>
<P>3. Nightbane, Sword of the Valiant - One of the best ratio's around and a very very nice clicky.</P>
<P>4. Dawnseeker's Chestpiece of the Defender - Stats alone explain it all</P>
<P>5. Valorium Belt of Devotion - Who cares if we don't need it. Aggro mods ftw</P>
				
